{
  "texts": [
    "Although these methods have achieved leaps in accuracy, they rely on large-scale document indices [57,187] and cannot be optimized in an end-to-end way.",
    "Moreover, when people search for information, what they really need is a precise and reliable answer.",
    "This document ranking list-based IR approach still requires users to spend time summarizing their required answers, which is not ideal enough for information seeking [195].With the development of Transformer-based pre-trained language models such as T5 [231], BART [138], and GPT [228], they have demonstrated their strong text generation capabilities.",
    "In recent years, large language models (LLMs) have brought about revolutionary changes in the field of AI-generated content (AIGC) [19,359].",
    "Based on large pre-training corpora and advanced training techniques like RLHF [36], LLMs [8,105,209,286] have made significant progress in natural language tasks, such as dialogue [209,282] and question answering [174,225]."
  ]
}